The paper deals with machine learning algorithms and optimization of performance measures, which are common topics in the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of classifiers and the focus on image classification tasks suggest that the paper could also fit in the sub-category of cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also mentions the contingency table and AUC, which are commonly used in the sub-categories of cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
